The paper discusses a framework for multi-domain and multi-task learning using both tensor and neural network perspectives. The paper's focus on machine learning and neural networks suggests that it is likely to belong to the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
